      "weather": "FINE",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IN THE QUEUE (3) settled back but wound up strongly to hit the frame when third (23.46) at The Gardens in Grade 5. Missed the placings only try here. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Can find winning form. ASTON ROJA (2) produced a modest effort most recently when seventh at The Gardens over 272m behind Young Energy (16.73) in a Grade 4/5. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. HECTIC BLUE (4) has shown good improvement at her last two starts, finishing in the money last time when 2nd at Gunnedah over 340m. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Hard to beat again. INVISIBLE MAN (1) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can atone.",
